{"tid":2317658,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"壹傳媒逾4億港元出售台灣物業","createTime":"2020-12-08T18:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T14:12:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8fec5adefa0f7e7791672f5bbaa5f776c0dfcdad","tid":2317658,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T18:23:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564278-20201208.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564278-20201208.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W%2Bf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=8d64629b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564278-20201208.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=67b964ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564278-20201208.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒公布，以17.5億元新台幣，折合約4.76億港元，出售台灣物業予遊戲開發商網銀國際。<br />\n<br />\n公告指，位於台北的整棟建築物連同92個車位，總面積約1.53萬平方公尺。物業主要用於集團台灣業務營運，小部份出租予一名獨立第三方。物業將於成交時按「現狀」形式交吉 。<br />\n<br />\n公司指，出售所得款項淨額約4.62億港元，將改善集團整體現金狀況，以作為一般營運資金及供未來可能出現的商機之用。出售後，集團租金收入將每年減少約230萬港元，預期以所得款項償還若干銀行借貸後，集團融資成本將每年減少約480萬港元。"},{"pid":"f6a615015634883aad0d131d6201d1e4af0c9b94","tid":2317658,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8fec5adefa0f7e7791672f5bbaa5f776c0dfcdad","tid":2317658,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T18:23:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564278-20201208.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564278-20201208.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W%2Bf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=8d64629b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564278-20201208.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=67b964ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/